    <item>
      <title>Self-Developing Asset Management Platform Based On Symfony Framework</title>
      <link>/2016/self-developing-asset-management-platform-based-on-symfony-framework/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Nov 2016 17:54:13 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/2016/self-developing-asset-management-platform-based-on-symfony-framework/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;根據公司直屬領導指示，進行 &lt;strong&gt;資產管理系統平臺&lt;/strong&gt; 的開發，整個項目由本人獨立完成，項目週期2個月左右，現已部署上線，可通過公司內網訪問。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;因本人此前從事&lt;a href=&#34;https://secure.php.net&#34; title=&#34;PHP is a popular general-purpose scripting language that is especially suited to web development.&#34;&gt;PHP&lt;/a&gt;開發，故選擇&lt;a href=&#34;https://secure.php.net&#34; title=&#34;PHP is a popular general-purpose scripting language that is especially suited to web development.&#34;&gt;PHP&lt;/a&gt;做爲開發語言，開發框架選擇&lt;a href=&#34;https://symfony.com&#34; title=&#34;High Performance PHP Framework for Web Development&#34;&gt;Symfony&lt;/a&gt;。如何部署Symfony項目，詳見本人 &lt;a href=&#34;/2016/configuring-nginx-web-server-for-symfony-framework-on-gnu-linux/&#34;&gt;blog&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Configuring Nginx Web Server For Symfony Framework On GNU Linux</title>
      <link>/2016/configuring-nginx-web-server-for-symfony-framework-on-gnu-linux/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Nov 2016 17:18:20 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/2016/configuring-nginx-web-server-for-symfony-framework-on-gnu-linux/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://symfony.com&#34; title=&#34;High Performance PHP Framework for Web Development&#34;&gt;Symfony&lt;/a&gt;是一款&lt;a href=&#34;https://secure.php.net&#34; title=&#34;PHP is a popular general-purpose scripting language that is especially suited to web development.&#34;&gt;PHP&lt;/a&gt;開發框架，具體安裝、配置可參閱本人之前 &lt;a href=&#34;/2016/installing-and-setting-up-the-symfony-framework-on-centos-7/&#34;&gt;blog&lt;/a&gt;。本文記錄如何在&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nginx.com&#34; title=&#34;High Performance Load Balancer, Web Server, &amp;amp; Reverse Proxy&#34;&gt;Nginx&lt;/a&gt;中部署&lt;a href=&#34;https://symfony.com&#34; title=&#34;High Performance PHP Framework for Web Development&#34;&gt;Symfony&lt;/a&gt;項目。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;說明&lt;/strong&gt;：文中的操作、配置基於&lt;a href=&#34;https://symfony.com&#34; title=&#34;High Performance PHP Framework for Web Development&#34;&gt;Symfony 3&lt;/a&gt;（2016年11月），不一定適用於&lt;a href=&#34;https://symfony.com&#34; title=&#34;High Performance PHP Framework for Web Development&#34;&gt;Symfony 4&lt;/a&gt;。此次遷移只做勘誤，不做具體配置的更新（2018年04月16日）。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>LEMP Stack Installation And Configuration On CentOS 7</title>
      <link>/2016/lemp-stack-installation-and-configuration-on-centos-7/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Mar 2016 18:31:58 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/2016/lemp-stack-installation-and-configuration-on-centos-7/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This article documents how to install, configure &lt;strong&gt;LEMP&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nginx.com&#34; title=&#34;High Performance Load Balancer, Web Server, &amp;amp; Reverse Proxy&#34;&gt;Nginx&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mysql.com&#34; title=&#34;MySQL is the world&#39;s most popular open source database.&#34;&gt;MySQL&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&#34;https://secure.php.net&#34; title=&#34;PHP is a popular general-purpose scripting language that is especially suited to web development.&#34;&gt;PHP&lt;/a&gt;) stack in &lt;code&gt;CentOS 7&lt;/code&gt; which &lt;code&gt;SELinux&lt;/code&gt;、&lt;code&gt;Firewalld&lt;/code&gt; has been enabled.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I wrote some shell script to automate operation, the project is hosted on &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/MaxdSre/axd-ShellScript&#34; title=&#34;axd Shell Script&#34;&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;. But &lt;a href=&#34;https://secure.php.net&#34; title=&#34;PHP is a popular general-purpose scripting language that is especially suited to web development.&#34;&gt;PHP&lt;/a&gt; is still need to installed manually currently.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>在CentOS 7中配置LEMP開發環境全記錄</title>
      <link>/2016/lemp-stack-installation-and-configuration-on-centos-7/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Mar 2016 18:31:58 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/2016/lemp-stack-installation-and-configuration-on-centos-7/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;本文記錄如何在已啓用&lt;code&gt;SELinux&lt;/code&gt;、&lt;code&gt;Firewalld&lt;/code&gt;防火牆的&lt;code&gt;CentOS 7&lt;/code&gt;系統中安裝、配置 &lt;strong&gt;LEMP&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nginx.com&#34; title=&#34;High Performance Load Balancer, Web Server, &amp;amp; Reverse Proxy&#34;&gt;Nginx&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mysql.com&#34; title=&#34;MySQL is the world&#39;s most popular open source database.&#34;&gt;MySQL&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&#34;https://secure.php.net&#34; title=&#34;PHP is a popular general-purpose scripting language that is especially suited to web development.&#34;&gt;PHP&lt;/a&gt;)套件。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;本人寫了一些Shell腳本用以實現操作的自動化，項目代碼託管在&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/MaxdSre/axd-ShellScript&#34; title=&#34;axd Shell Script&#34;&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;。已實現 系統初始化，&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nginx.com&#34; title=&#34;High Performance Load Balancer, Web Server, &amp;amp; Reverse Proxy&#34;&gt;Nginx&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mysql.com&#34; title=&#34;MySQL is the world&#39;s most popular open source database.&#34;&gt;MySQL&lt;/a&gt;的腳本化操作，但&lt;a href=&#34;https://secure.php.net&#34; title=&#34;PHP is a popular general-purpose scripting language that is especially suited to web development.&#34;&gt;PHP&lt;/a&gt;暫時仍需要手動安裝。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
